  <scopecontent id="aspace_4e494442fce3b9071669d3278d985c25">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Speeches, reports, pamphlets, newsletters, flyers, and unpublished items written or distributed by left wing organizations. Includes pamphlets by Upton Sinclair and Sumner H. Slichter; newsletters of the League for Independent Political Action; flyers of the Socialist Party; and material concerning women's political issues.</p>  </scopecontent>
